  </intervention>
  <intervention>
    <intervention_type>Behavioral</intervention_type>
    <intervention_name>step2: biomarkers of gamblers/gamers</intervention_name>
    <description>For each arm, subjects were divided into 2 groups: dependant or not dependant gamblers/gamers. Investigators focused on decision-making biomarkers following the following flow-chart:
psychiatric assesment and
registration of brain activity during a decision-making task in conditions of uncertainty (IGT) with its version for HR-EEG validated by investigators (Giustiniani, 2015).</description>
    <arm_group_label>online poker gamblers</arm_group_label>
    <arm_group_label>casino gamblers</arm_group_label>
